{"tid":285592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東方日報確認兩個事實  評論已故人士指引","createTime":"2017-06-16T03:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T06:51:17.000Z","uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"985cf5335c727e874c64b88088e549bb6c289a3e","tid":285592,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:06:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/6nlat018r/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2F6nlat018r%2Fimage.jpg&h=cc260b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東方日報確認左2個事實：<br />\n(1) 已故人士係東方日報創辦人；及<br />\n(2) 已故人士人士係不能提出誹謗訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n即係話「已故人士係東方日報創辦人」呢句本身, 就唔會構成誹謗, 或乜春「借題發揮」, 係佢自己都承認既！<br />\n<br />\n同埋最重要一點，係「 已故人士人士係不能提出誹謗訴訟」！東方日報仲走去搵個大狀, 去再次確認呢一點！<br />\n<br />\n當然啦, 呢個係common law黎架嘛！<br />\n<br />\n至於點解大家一提及已故人士, 唯獨呢份報紙咁大反應呢？<br />\n其他傳媒係who's fucking care呢?<br />\n我鬼知咩！"},{"pid":"258f4ab06605763ed895e90a48187ee35ca9bdab","tid":285592,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f4760b265e8bf4b4f561bcbd1f6c2b398dfdff","tid":285592,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:35:22.000Z","msg":"對比返6月15日篇報導, 就可以見到<br />\n之前係無提及呢D事實架<br />\n<br />\n突然間, 加返2段入去, 點解呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170615/mobile/odn-20170615-0615_00176_040.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170615%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20170615-0615_00176_040.html&d=BAGSEZDZK7E%2BO3%2BVeop%2F%2B9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=458309ce\" t